Origins: After several years of online hoaxes falsely proclaiming that the current date matches the future date visited by Marty McFly via the time-traveling DeLorean automobile in the 1989 film Back to the Future Part II , that day is finally upon us 21 October 2015:
Description: The Back to the Future Countdown Clock provides up-to-the-minute tracking of the time remaining before Marty McFly's return from the past.
Claim: Marty McFly's visit to the future occurs on 21 October 2015.
